longBusinessSummary: Capital VC Limited is a principal investment firm. It principally invests in listed and unlisted companies in Hong Kong and the People's Republic of China. It is formerly known as Sino Katalytics Investment Corporation. Capital VC Limited is based in Central, Hong Kong with additional office in Cayman Islands.
